<item>
            <title>[FELIX-2850] PackageAdmin return fragments / hosts even if the host isn&apos;t resolved</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-2850</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It seems fragments are attached before the resolution when the fragment is installed and PackageAdmin uses this information, so it will return those fragments even if the host isn&apos;t (or can&apos;t be) resolved.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12499008">FELIX-2850</key>
            <summary>PackageAdmin return fragments / hosts even if the host isn&apos;t resolved</summary>
